                                                        class="text">info@yourdomain.com</span></a></li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
                                <p>
                                    Copyright &copy;
